<ul><H1>   MY GRADUATE STUDIES AT UIUC</H1></ul><p>
<p>
<p>
<img src="Images/line_blue_marble.gif"><p>
<p>
<p>
<ul>
	Let's face it.  I will start my graduate studies at <a
href="http://www.uiuc.edu/index.html">UIUC</a> in the fall of 1995.  So
right now, I don't know many interesting facts about this area of the
world.  In six months to a year, I'm sure this page will improve
dramatically.  =)<p> <p>
 
	Right now, I know that I will be a student in the <a
href="http://ne43.ne.uiuc.edu/Nuclear/">Nuclear Engineering
Department</a>.  I'll be working in the <a
href="http://starfire.ne.uiuc.edu/pmi/pmi.html">Plasma-Material
Interaction Group</a> which judging from its homepage consists of an
exciting group of people.<p>


