<TITLE> BIG TIME </TITLE>
</head>
<body>
<font size="+1">
Name of Brewer: Roger Meredith <br>
Name of Brew: BIG TIME <br>
Category: Brown Ale <br>
Subcategory: American Brown <br>
Recipe type: All-Grain <br>
Club Affiliation: CIBA <br>
<p>
The Recipe: <br></font>
Number of Gallons Brewed: 5 <br>
Water Treatment: 1 tsp gypsum <br>
Yeast: Liquid<br>
Starter?: No<br>
Brand and Type: Wyeast 1056 American Ale<br>
Yeast Nutrients: none<br>
Carbonation (type): forced<br>
Amount: 23 psi<br>
Use of kegs?: yes<br>
Boiling Time: 90 min<br>
Gravities: OG=1.053, FG=1.016 <br>
