<head>
<TITLE> Ghandi's Butt </TITLE>
</head>
<body>
<font size="+1">
Name of Brewer: Eric Dallmann <br>
Name of Brew: Ghandi's Butt<br>
Category: English Style Pale Ale <br>
Subcategory:  India Pale Ale<br>
Recipe type: All-Grain <br>
Club Affiliation: Beer Nuts <br>
<p>
The Recipe: <br></font>
Water Treatment: 2 tsp Burton on Trent salts <br>
Yeast: Liquid<br>
Brand and Type: Wyeast 1056 <br>
Yeast Nutrients: none <br>
Carbonation (type): keg <br>
Boiling Time: 60 min <br>
Gravities: OG=1.048, FG=1.008 <br>
