<title> BUZZ 2nd Annual BrewOff Results </title>
<center>

<h2> Results of the Second Annual BUZZ Boneyard Brew-Off </h2>
<h3> Held July 20, 1996 at Joe's Brewery in Champaign, IL</h3>
<h4> 134 entries </h4>
<br>
<table border=5>
<tr><th colspan=4 align=center> <font size="+2"> Best of Show </th></tr>
 <tr>
 <th align=center> Person </th>
 <th align=center> Style </th>
 <th align=center> City, State </th>
 <th align=center> Club </th>
 </tr>
