<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Wyeast Temperature Ranges
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2 ALIGN = "center">Wyeast Preferred Temperature Ranges </H2>
<HR>
<P>

This document contains tables showing the preferred fermentation
temperature ranges for Wyeast strains.  It was assembled from
information provided in a pamphlet by Wyeast.
<p>

