<center><h1>Natural Gas, Oil and Coal</h1>
<BR>
Lecture-Discussion # 14
<BR>
Nuclear Engineering 201
<BR>
Professor Ruzic
<P></CENTER>
<H2>Introduction</H2>
<P>
 We already covered how much of these resources exist and how
they are used.  This lecture-discussion looks at exactly what
fossil fuels are, how they are extracted, and how they are refined.
 We will also look at recent advances in these techniques with
an eye to future developments.
<P>
