href="http://www.astro.washington.edu/strobel/star-sun.notes/star-sun.notes.html
>The Sun and Stellar Structure <a/><P>
<a href="http://nrelinfo.nrel.gov/research/pv/us.html">Photovoltaics</a><P>
<HR></center><H2>  Questions or comments?</H2><P>
