<DOCNO>WT08-B26-83</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA041-000766-B026-369</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://starfire.ne.uiuc.edu:80/ne201/webproject/lehner/ICFindir.html 128.174.200.146 19970303040615 text/html 1604
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 03 Mar 1997 04:03:17 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Mon, 11 Dec 1995 17:54:58 GMT
