<DOCNO>WT08-B26-85</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA041-000766-B026-399</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://starfire.ne.uiuc.edu:80/ne201/webproject/lehner/ICFgov.html 128.174.200.146 19970303040644 text/html 2888
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 03 Mar 1997 04:03:45 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
