<head>	
<title> Current Technology </Title>
</head>

<body link=#0000FF text=#000000 background="backgrnd/screen.jpg">

<a name="start"></a>

<hr size=3 width=45%>
<h1 align="center">  Current Technology  </h1>
<hr size=3 width=45%>

<br>
<br>
<br>

<p>Despite the positive early predictions regarding fast breeder reactors, the current situation is far from the ideal case.  The Liquid Metal Fast Breeder Reactor (LMFBR) predominates as the current design.  Various specific projects such as the remarkable Integral Fast Reactor (IFR), the large French Superphenix Fast Reactor, and the relatively new Japanese Monju fast breeder reactor all employ the basic LMFBR process.  The following sections illustrate the &quot;Current Technology&quot; of fast breeder reactors.  Furthermore, the current economic situation and miscellaneous advances in breeder technology that have been achieved recently and continue to influence current design are identified.</p> 

<p>
<img src="icons/gls_ball.gif"><a href="lmfbr.html">Liquid Metal Fast Breeder Reactor (LMFBR)</a><br><br>

<img src="icons/gls_ball.gif"><a href="ifr.html">Integral Fast Reactor (IFR)</a><br><br>

<img src="icons/gls_ball.gif"><a href="sphenix.html">French Superphenix Breeder Reactor</a><br><br>

<img src="icons/gls_ball.gif"><a href="monju.html">Japanese Monju Breeder Reactor</a><br><br>

<img src="icons/gls_ball.gif"><a href="econ2.html">Current Economics of the FBR</a><br><br>

<img src="icons/gls_ball.gif"><a href="miscell.html">Miscellaneous Advances</a><br>

<br>
<br>
<hr size=5>
<br>

<p>
<a href="#start"> <img src="icons/up.gif"> <i> Return to the top of this page.</i></a></p>

<p>
<a href="lmfbr.html"> <img src="icons/right.gif"> <i> Proceed to &quot;Liquid Metal Fast Breeder Reactor (LMFBR).&quot;</i></a></p>

<p>
<a href="history.html"> <img src="icons/left.gif"> <i> Return to the &quot;History&quot; main page.</i></a></p>

<p>
