<head>	
<title> Diagram of Fast Breeder Test Reactor (FBTR) </Title>
</head>

<body link=#0000FF text=#000000 bgcolor=#FFFFFF>

<a name="start"></a>

<hr size=3 width=70%>
<h2 align="center">  Diagram of Fast Breeder Test Reactor (FBTR)  </h2>
<hr size=3 width=70%>

<br>
<br>
<center><img src="breaks/colors2.gif"></center>
<br>
<br>

<center><img src="images/fbtr.jpg" align=center valign=middle
	border=1 alt="Detailed Diagram of the FBTR"></center>

