<HEAD>
<TITLE>How much do they cost</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#FF3333" VLINK="#FFFFFF" ALINK="#FFFFFF">

<h1><CENTER><I>Electric Cars<BR>How much do they cost?</I></CENTER></h1>
<p>
<HR size=1>

<TEXTAREA NAME="" ROWS="" COLS="">Electric vehicles are currently more expensive than traditional gasoline automobiles.  However, as production of electric vehicles increases, this cost should decrease.  In fact, it should eventually be financially competitive with gasoline cars.</TEXTAREA>

</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT08-B26-147</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA042-000771-B040-163</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://starfire.ne.uiuc.edu:80/ne201/webproject/jennings/hydro.html 128.174.200.146 19970303022224 text/html 23750
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 03 Mar 1997 02:19:24 GMT
