<head><tittle>Conclusion</tittle></head>
<body background="rain.gif">
<center><h1>Conclusion</h1></center><p>
<font size=4>	Windmills are an excellent way to produce electricity without 
polluting the environment. It has an advantage to be install in faster 
time without worrying about expensive installations comparing to fosil-fuels.
Windmills can work only efficiently in places where there is a lot of wind. 
These winds has to be from 7 miles to 14 miles per hour or  more all year 
round. There is a incredible wind resources in different parts of the 
world: England, US California, Asia, and India and other 
places. </font size=4><p>
