<P><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=+1>Three Mile Island was a nuclear
power plant near<alink="#1111ff"> <A 
HREF="http://dsknepper.nuce.psu.edu:2112/~sdb113/psuans.html">Harrisburg,
Pennsylvania.</A>  The power plant consisted of pressurized water 
reactors, 
which are types of <a  href="light_water.html">light-water reactors</a>.  
