   <TITLE>[Def]Light Water</TITLE>
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.0Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="yellow_rock.gif">

<H1>Light Water</H1>

<P>
<HR>Light water is what is considered usual water. The hydrogen in light
water contains no neutrons. <A HREF="http://starfire.ne.uiuc.edu/ne201/webproject/ijuin/heavy_water.html">Heavy
water</A>, on the other hand, contain hydrogen with a neutron. 
<HR></P>

