<h3>
Powders -<p>
</h3>
<h2><dd>The exact mix and chemical makeup of the is dependent on a whole host of variables. <p>
<ul>
<li>The purity of the atmosphere in the heater or boiler.<p>
<li>The gas or water used inside of the nozzle.<p>
<li>The purity of the cooling agent that cools the molten metal as it leaves the nozzle.)<p>

<a href="http://www.cen.uiuc.edu/~mneumann/pwder1.jpg">Chart 1 of Powders.</a><p>
