<br>UTILITY USES
<br>
<hr>
<br>Utility loads are the highest during the day due to commercial and industrial facilities. <br>This corresponds to the time when photovoltaic cells produce electricity.  Large <br>photovoltaic arrays can be installed to supplement the conventional power plant <br>needs.  Arrays can also be built near the customers to remove the need to upgrade or <br>build additional T&D lines.
