<h3>
Thermal Spraying - 
<dd> The process of  coating a material through the use of particulate deposition which are molten, semi-molten, or solid particles and are deposited on to a substrate.<p>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT08-B26-236</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA041-000766-B023-280</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://starfire.ne.uiuc.edu:80/ne201/96webprojects/pradosev/Document.html 128.174.200.146 19970303035010 text/html 3473
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 03 Mar 1997 03:47:13 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Last-modified: Mon, 28 Oct 1996 21:58:40 GMT
