<Body BACKGROUND="stucco.gif">

<h3>
Plasma -
<dd>A collection of charged particles containing about equal numbers of positive ions and electrons and exhibiting some properties of a gas but differing from a gas in being a good conductor of electricity and in being affected by a magnetic field.<p>

<a href=" http://www.lycos.com/cgi-bin/pursuit?query=Plasmas">Plasma Links </a>
