<a href="#future">Future for the Telecommunications/Electronics Superhighway Era: Highlighting Traffic Patterns, Transmission Systems</a><br>
<a href="#digital">Digital Video Networking</a><br>
<a href="#wireless">Wireless Communications--Update</a><br>
