<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Business Communications Company</TITLE></HEAD><IMG
SRC="bccLogo3.gif"><P><body>Since 1971,
Business Communications Company, Inc. (BCC) has published Business Opportunity
Reports, newsletters and magazines
in the fields of biotechnology, energy, telecommunications, chemicals,
separations, engineering and food processing.
Our diverse client list includes major companies in these fields in the United
States and overseas. BCC also is well-known
for its annual conferences in plastics, membranes, biotechnology and
energy.<P>BCC specializes in the analysis of new
and emerging technology.  By combining science/technology and business
perspectives, we provide a realistic, timely
analysis of events which play a part in getting products onto the market and
keeping them there.  Our staff
of marketing and technology analysts consider new information, changing
directions, market dynamics, economics,
customer attitudes, alternative technologies and marketability.<P>Here you will
find information on BCC's in-depth
and critically acclaimed market analyses and monthly newsletters covering a
broad range of technologies, as well as our
scheduled conferences. All provide a wealth of important information for
executives, sales and marketing personnel,
researchers, and investment specialists.<P>BCC...the place to come for the
hard-to-find information you need.<P>
<HR size=3>
