<b><a name = "P-225" href="bcc_order_report.html">P-225   Polyolefin
Copolymers</a></b><br>

This new BCC report is a study and survey of the past, current, and projected products,
technology and market for polyolefin copolymers based on polyethylene and polypopylene
chemistry.  It shows how copolymers were developed to meet special needs not available in the
respective homopolymers and how these developments opened markets for products with uses
extending beyond normal thermoplastic processing such as extrusion and molding.  It covers
technology and markets for LDPE process bases on high and low pressure plants, along with
