Wastes, Wastewater, and Municipal Waste</a></b><br>

This comprehensive BCC technical-economic report evaluates the U.S. markets for microbial
environmental management.  Although bioremediation of hazardous wastes are stressed, the
scope of the report includes aerobic and anaerobic wastewater and sludge digestion, microbial oil
spill remediation, and energy recovery from municipal waste.  Five- and ten-year projections for
market activity and value are provided.  Industry structure, associations within the biotechnology
industry, pricing trends, R&D, environmental influences, competition with other environmental
management technologies and companies are included in this unique market study.<br>
Target Date: <b>December 1996 </b>                                         Prepublication Price:
<b>$2850.000</b><P>

