experiencing rising demand.  The
increasingly stringent environmental regulations for water quality will also stimulate demand for
sensors, monitors and
related instrumentation.  This innovative BCC report investigates the problems and opportunities
for these unique
devices in the industrial, commercial, residential and municipal markets.  The full range of pH
electrodes, meters and
controllers, as well as conductivity meters, nitrate meters, oxygen analyzers, and
wastewater/groundwater samplers are
examined.  Profiles of major corporate players are provided, along with market projections for
this evolving
marketplace.<br>
Published <b>December 1996</b>                 Prepublication Price: <b>$2850.00</b>


