<b><A NAME = "C-147RA" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-147RA  Industrial and Chemical Applications</b></A><BR>
The first part in the BCC Enzyme Series covers applications for enzymes in the following industry sectors: food and beverage; detergents; textiles; leather; chemical synthesis; and chiral technology.<br>
Published <b>July 1994</b> 223 pages  
