<b><A NAME = "C-147RB" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-147RB  Specialty and Medical Applications</b></A><BR>
The second part of the BCC Enzyme Series details analytical uses for enzymes, including substrate analysis, enzyme reporter tags for immunoassays and gene probes, enzyme standards and controls, and enzymes for sample preparation.  Biotechnology applications, including nucleic acid manipulation, tissue and cell treatment, protein manipulation, glycobiology and purification, also are considered.<br>
Published <b>July 1994</b> 241 pages  
