<b><A NAME = "C-147RC" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-147RC  Comprehensive Enzymes Directory</b></A><BR>
The final part of the BCC Enzymes Trilogy provides detailed information on over 300 common and rare enzymes used worldwide. Enzyme statistics are cross-referenced vis--vis profiles of over 126 domestic and international companies active in enzyme research, manufacture and supply.<br>
Published <b>July 1994</b> 95 pages 
