<b><A NAME = "C-009X" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-009X Structural and Specialty Adhesives</b></a><BR>
This BCC technical-market analysis of the $1.86 billion structural and specialty adhesives industry focuses on formulations that have found markets based on their unique properties or applications.  New and established markets are identified and quantified with projections for business opportunities and forecasts through 1995.  New polymers and high-performance materials and adhesive systems are examined in detail with an assessment of key issues such as properties, performance rating, environmental and other regulatory concerns, manufacturers and suppliers. <br>
Published <b>February 1991</b>  200 pages  
