<b><A NAME = "C-132B" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-132B  Sorbent Materials:  Technical Review</b></a><BR>
As a supplement to <a href="#C-132A">C-132A</a>, this BCC volume provides an accurate and informative analysis of sorption mechanisms and terminology. Absorption (also referred to as scrubbing) and adsorption are discussed in detail. Also covered are relevant process technologies, and the various sorbent materials available, with their specific applications. This unique volume provides an insightful and comprehensive patent and literature review which will maximize your awareness of current developments occurring in the field of sorbent technology. This study highlights potential opportunities which will arise in the coming decade. <br>
