<b><A NAME = "C-133" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-133  Sorbent Materials for Spills and Other Liquid Pickups</b></a><BR>
This BCC analysis details the markets and technologies for the variety of absorption materials in the synthetic, mineral, and organic categories.  Applications covered include industrial spill cleanup and containment, floodwater pickup, and others in the personal hygiene, household, and medical areas.  The report provides estimates and forecasts of materials consumption within each application market for the next five-year period.  The comprehensive study describes the industry structure, indentifies its players, analyzes the economics and pricing criteria, lists patents and R&D efforts, considers the effects of environmental and safety issues; and assesses the dynamics of international markets and players. <br> 
