<b><A NAME = "C-134" HREF="bcc_order_report.html">C-134  Chlorofluorocarbons (CFCs): Alternatives (In-Kind) and Substitutes (Not-in-Kind)</b></a><BR>
This BCC technical-economic report evaluates the markets for commercial fluorine compounds as represented by the chlorofluorocarbons (CFCs), fluoropolymers, and the alternatives to CFCs. High-tech markets and new niche markets  are identified and quantified. The worldwide problems of production and use of these chemicals in light of environmental mandates are analyzed. The report includes insights and perceptions offered by the producers and suppliers interviewed.<br>
