<b> <A NAME = "P-122R" HREF="bcc_order_report.html"> P-122R  Hose and Tubing Markets</b> </a><BR>
Hose and tubing are used in a wide variety of industries ranging from automotive to construction and aerospace.  This BCC report on the hose and tubing industry discusses and quantifies the materials used by hose manufacturers by hose industry classification and applications. Included is a review of thermoset rubbers, engineering and commodity resins such as teflon and PVC, as well as alloys and thermoplastic elastomers. The hose and tubing industry is also classified by type of hose. This comprehensive report identifies market trends, competitive dynamics, and technological developments in this industry. Statistics are presented on materials by major industry use and sub-applications. Major hose producer market shares and product concentrations are also provided. <br>
